==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ortygan
<hw>Or"ty*gan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, <?/, a
quail.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of several species of East
Indian birds of the genera <gen>Ortygis</gen> and <gen>Hemipodius</gen>.
They resemble quails, but lack the hind toe. See
<er>Turnix</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

